title: Jenelle Evans's New Video of Baby Ensley Shows Where Her Heart Is
text:
Jenelle Evans's New Video of Baby Ensley Shows Where Her Heart Is Jenny Erikson 
j_evans1219/Instagram Get ready for a major dose of cuteness, because here it comes. Jenelle Evans shared a video of baby Ensley , and it's absolutely precious. Of course the thing that makes it extra special is that it's all about the family love. 
The Teen Mom 2 star shared the sweet moment on Instagram of her fianc√© David Eason snuggling with their daughter, along with her eldest son Jace, 7. We're sure that 2-year-old Kaiser was running around somewhere nearby! A post shared by Jenelle Evans (@j_evans1219) on Feb 18, 2017 at 4:57am PST 
Little Ensley Jolie made her appearance on January 24. She is Jenelle's first child with David, as well as her first daughter. David also has two children from previous relationships. 
More from CafeMom: Jenelle Evans Shows Off a Close-Up of Her New Engagement Ring 
It's been a busy few weeks for Jenelle -- not only has she been adjusting to being a mom of three, she's also newly engaged! Dave popped the question earlier this month, and she proudly showed off her massive engagement ring on social media. 
No word on a wedding date yet, but we have a feeling they're not going to rush things. After all, it's obvious they're just taking their time enjoying their sweet little family right now.
